/**
 * DashboardContent - Premium World-Class Redesign
 *
 * Design Philosophy: "Informed Simplicity with Intelligence"
 * - Hero metric dominates for instant comprehension
 * - 5W2H recommendations for premium users (confidence tier)
 * - Outcome tracking access to prove recommendation value
 * - Tier-aware progressive disclosure
 * - Smooth, physics-based animations throughout
 *
 * Architecture:
 * - FREE: Wellness score + basic tracking cards
 * - BASIC: + Nutri-Score + daily summaries
 * - PREMIUM: + 5W2H recommendations + predictions + outcome tracking
 */

